Name:           calendar-recycling
Version:        0.0
Release:        0
Summary:        List years with the same calendars
Group:          Development/Libraries/Haskell

License:        BSD-3-Clause
Url:            https://hackage.haskell.org/package/%{name}
Source0:        https://hackage.haskell.org/package/%{name}-%{version}/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz

BuildRequires:  ghc-Cabal-devel
BuildRequires:  ghc-rpm-macros
BuildRequires:  ghc-containers-devel
BuildRequires:  ghc-html-devel
BuildRequires:  ghc-old-time-devel
BuildRequires:  ghc-utility-ht-devel

%description
Generate a partial HTML document grouping years by the pattern of the calender.
The program respects the starting weekday of a year and the existence of a leap
day, but it ignores the date of the Easter festival.


